headline: P&G to Webcast Presentation From the Barclays Global Consumer Staples Conference, September 4, 2025
summary: CINCINNATI, August 28, 2025--Jon R. Moeller, Chairman of the Board, President and Chief Executive Officer and Andre Schulten, Chief Financial Officer of The Procter & Gamble Company (NYSE:PG) will be featured speakers at the Barclays Global Consumer Staples Conference on Thursday, September 4, 2025, at 8:15 a.m. ET (Eastern Time).
